criterion_text: Eastern Cooperative Technology Group (ECOG) performance status of 0,1 or 2.
ECOG performance status greater than or equal to 2
Eastern Cooperative Oncology Group (ECOG) performance status and/or other performance status 0, 1, or 2
Performance status must be ECOG PS 0, 1, or 2.
ECOG performance score of 2 or greater
ECOG performance status of ≤ 2 at study entry
Clinical performance status of ECOG 0 or 1.
ECOG performance status score between 0-3 (TAPS study)
Eastern Cooperative Oncology Group (ECOG) performance status of 0-3.
ECOG performance status of zero, one, or two.
ECOG performance status score of 2 or less
